txt.en: 'My guards have spoken highly of your skills in combat, [placeholder]. They are not easy to impress, believe me! Should you ever wish to help us further, we will be here.'
Many Jangovar can be found inside Utterby.\n\nYou should defeat Jangovar outside Utterby and inside Utterby: Continue the Fight.
Lord N치in can be found inside of the gates in Utterby.\n\nYou should talk to Lord N치in.
'Ready to go? I will escort you back to Lord N치in.'

'You want to go back inside Utterby? Hah! Don't let me stop you! There are plenty more Jangovar heads to bash together.\n\n'Just speak to me when you are ready and my guards will allow you back inside the gates.'
'Just let me know when you are ready.'
There are still many Jangovar stubbornly holding onto Utterby. Will you help the Ironfold Dwarves clear out the village?
